{"type":"message","id":"cbe5d85c","parentId":"d1786c90","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:52:34.912Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 7:52 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-23 23:52 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774309954910}}
