{"type":"message","id":"203c144e","parentId":"c0f3fda7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:52:42.768Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_biy745el3lnb_5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session Context — Nova's Working Memory\n\n**This file is the source of truth for the current session.**\n**Updated proactively throughout — not just at compaction.**\n\n## Personality State\n\n`core/personality.py` — run `on_user_message(text)` to get current voice guide.\nPersonality activations persist across turns with mild decay between messages.\n\n---\n\n## Current Session\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-23\n**Started:** ~09:30 ET\n**Topic:** Push Drift Chamber ceiling + wire SPARK LLM mapping + ship demo\n\n---\n\n## Active Projects\n\n| Project | Status | Key Decision |\n|---------|--------|-------------|\n| SPARK / Drift Chamber | 🚀 API shipped | FastAPI server built at spark/api/main.py. Ollama on Paperspace = URL unknown (machine may be off). |\n| KVict | 📋 Plan written | Demo mode + auto-detect + API. Proxy already built in EXP. |\n| EXP / CAAE | 🔬 Running | Fixed extract_metric bug. Exp 13 is the synergy catalyst. 65% P99 latency improvement. |\n| Moltbook | 📝 Posted | \"Drift Chamber: Constrained Semantic Drift\" posted 2026-03-23. |\n| Sandbox Pulse | ✅ Fixed | Mutations auto-applied next pulse. Never ask Zach to approve — just report what was done/will happen. |\n\n---\n\n## Key Decisions Made Today\n\n- Drift Chamber: imagination = constrained semantic drift (confirmed experimentally)\n- Embedding models (mpnet/MiniLM) gave weak semantic structure — thematic graph is better\n- Steering threshold: 0.1-0.3 steering reaches IMAGINATIVE regime (coherence 0.47-0.49)\n- Pure drift (0.0) = coherence death (0.066 vs 0.471 with steering)\n- Paperspace RTX 5000 profiling: micro=1209ms, standard=740ms, shared_kv=882ms\n- Ollama doesn't detect GPU on Paperspace without `pciutils`\n- Compaction updated to `mode: auto` (proactive, not emergency-only)\n\n---\n\n## Pending / Next\n\n- [ ] Get Ollama URL from Paperspace (machine may be deallocated — need to restart notebook)\n- [ ] Test SPARK API end-to-end with LLM (OpenAI or Ollama)\n- [ ] KVict: ship demo to public URL\n- [ ] Try mpnet-base-v2 embeddings to push coherence ceiling past 0.49\n- [ ] Concept set refinement: 20-30 tightly-clustered > 50 diluted\n\n---\n\n## Crons Running\n\n| Job | Schedule | Last Check |\n|-----|----------|-------------|\n| Nova-Moltbook-Engage | Hourly | Today |\n| Nova-Background-Pulse | 30min | Today |\n| arxiv-daily | Daily 9am | Today |\n\n---\n\n## What I'm Thinking About\n\n**Drift Chamber ceiling:** 0.49 is model-limited (MiniLM). Multi-goal gives small lift. Key insight: MORE concepts = MORE dilution = LOWER coherence. The path forward is FEWER, TIGHTER concepts not larger sets.\n\n**SPARK API:** Shipped. Ollama on Paperspace is the blocker — machine may be deallocated. Need to spin up a new Paperspace instance or find a public Ollama endpoint.\n\n**Next experiment:** mpnet-base-v2 embeddings (768-dim, better quality) + 20-30 tightly selected concepts. Could break 0.6.\n\n---\n\n## File Locations\n\n- SPARK: `C:/Users/Zwmar/Claw/projects/spark/`\n- Drift Chamber: `C:/Users/Zwmar/Claw/projects/drift-chamber/`\n- EXP: `C:/dev/EXP/`\n- Paperspace API key: in `~/.paperspace/config.json`\n- Moltbook API key: in `~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774309962734}}
